    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense from an environmental standpoint, but doesn't it feel like a bit of a trade-off? some people say that while it helps the planet, it basically just creates a tiered city where the wealthy can pay to drive and everyone else is squeezed. do you think the climate benefits actually justify the economic impact on working class commuters?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
